show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/k2Sc8H
show.description: In a remote tech center, a few people are forcibly confined, their memories erased, and their identities altered through experiments. Among them, a young woman begins to recall not only her true self but also the lost memory of her sister. Caught between betrayal, fear, and control, her fight is not just for freedom — but for family, identity, and justice too.
